data.text:
2020: Saw his first collegiate action in the Hokies' win over Virginia (12/12).

High School: Played for head coach Brad Butler at Shadow Creek High School in Pearland, Texas … The team is playing for the 5A state title at AT&T Stadium in Arlington, Texas on Dec. 21 … Ranks second on the squad with 16.0 TFL to go along with 45 total tackles (31 solo), 6.0 sacks and four forced fumbles … Team was the state runner-up in 2018, posting a 15-1 record … Earned first-team all-district honors as a junior … Ranked as the No. 13 weakside defensive end in the country by 247.com.
